## IEmbeddable.runtimeId property

Unique ID an embeddable is assigned each time it is initialized. This ID is different for different instances of the same embeddable. For example, if the same dashboard is rendered twice on the screen, all embeddable instances will have a unique `runtimeId`<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
readonly runtimeId?: number;
```
